HEADWORD: Dies non
<hw>Di"es non"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[L. <ets>dies non
juridicus</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A day on which courts are
not held, as Sunday or any legal holiday.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

